{
  "texts": [
    "They concluded that PLP could be helpful for low-resource Chinese DSR.",
    "LPCC is a representation of Linear Predictive Coding (LPC) in the cepstrum domain (Wong and Sridharan 2001).",
    "It uses the linear method to obtain acoustic information.",
    "Deqing (2010) proposed a specific Tibetan speech recognition system that discussed the experimental results of LPCC and MFCC.",
    "The system showed that both had a good performance for Tibetan acoustic features."
  ]
}